Name: Catorize
About the game: Catorize is the game that is bound to carry you away to the magical world of the good and the bad where you will meet the main hero of the story. Find out how you can become a part of the greatest heroic event and help to make the world bright and cheerful place to live in! Control the power of jump with one click. Change direction to help the cat catch the colour. 80+ levels, 5+ locations, more traps and other items! The resident of the magnificently wonderful world is waiting for your help!
